<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Produk Lokal Bali</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="font-body">
    <nav
      class="fixed top-0 z-30 w-screen text-black bg-white min-h-16 flex justify-between items-center px-14"
    >
      <h1 class="text-2xl uppercase">Produk Lokal Bali</h1>
      <div class="w-1/5 border-white flex justify-between self-center">
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#reviews">Reviews</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <main>
      <section
        id="home"
        class="items-center h-screen m-auto overflow-hidden font-body"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute z-20 flex flex-col text-center justify-center items-center h-screen text-white right-0 left-0 overflow-hidden"
        >
          <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded" />
          <h1 class="text-6xl my-3">Produk Lokal Bali</h1>
          <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded" />
          <p class="text-2xl mt-2 font-body">sederhana, namun kaya rasa</p>
        </div>
        <img src="../public/img/home-bg.jpg" alt="" class="w-screen h-auto" />
      </section>
      <section id="about" class="flex flex-col">
        <div class="h-64 flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-fixed overflow-hidden bg-no-repeat bg-cover relative" style="background-image: url(../public/img/about.jfif);">
          <div class="right-0 left-0 top-0 bottom-0 bg-black flex flex-col justify-center items-center opacity-65 absolute z-0"></div>
          <div class="absolute z-10 right-0 left-0 top-0 bottom-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded" />
            <h1 class="text-6xl my-3 text-center text-white">About</h1>
            <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded mx-auto"/>
          </div>        
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black px-32 py-14">
          <p class="text-lg leading-10 text-center text-white font-body">
            Website Produk Lokal Bali dikembangkan dengan tujuan utama untuk
            memperkenalkan kekayaan kuliner tradisional Bali, menampilkan
            beragam makanan dan minuman khas yang telah menjadi ciri khas pulau
            dewata. Melalui ulasan singkat yang disertakan, pengunjung dapat
            memahami lebih dalam tentang cita rasa unik yang ditawarkan oleh
            setiap hidangan tradisional Bali. Diharapkan, dengan kehadiran
            website ini, pengetahuan dan apresiasi terhadap warisan kuliner Bali
            akan semakin tersebar luas di kalangan masyarakat, serta memberikan
            dorongan bagi pengembangan dan pelestarian kekayaan budaya kuliner
            Indonesia.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="h-screen w-1/2 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="../img/kuwud removebg.png" alt="" class="m-auto" />
        </div> -->
        <!-- disini ada 2, sebelah kiri penjelasan dari kenapa webnya ini dibuat, sebelah kanan foto makanan/minuman -->
      </section>
      <section id="reviews" class="min-h-screen">
        <div class="h-64 flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-fixed bg-no-repeat	bg-cover relative" style="background-image: url(../public/img/reviews.jfif);">
          <div class="right-0 left-0 top-0 bottom-0 bg-black flex flex-col justify-center items-center opacity-65 absolute z-0"></div>
          <div class="absolute z-10 right-0 left-0 top-0 bottom-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded" />
            <h1 class="text-6xl my-3 text-center text-white">Reviews</h1>
            <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded mx-auto"/>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex shadow-xl my-10 mx-14">
          <div class="w-1/5 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="../public/img/IMG_20240413_115612.jpg" alt="" class="" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 w-4/5">
            <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl font-body">Paket Gurame Nyat-Nyat</h2>
            <h3 class="text-red-600 text-2xl">Rp50.000,00</h3>
            <h4 class="text-2xl">Kintamani, Bali</h4>
            <p class="text-transparent">Bintang 1234</p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-8">
              Paket Gurame Nyat-Nyat lengkap dengan gurame nyat-nyat khas
              Kintamani, plecing kangkung, dan teh manis. Gurame yang satu ini
              kaya rempah karena menggunakan paduan bawang, sereh, jahe, tomat
              hijau, lada hingga perasan jeruk nipis. Pemandangan langsung dari
              Gunung Batur pun kian menambahkan kesan pada makanan ini
            </p>
            <p class="text-base mt-10">Andini | nova.andini@gmail.com</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex shadow-xl mt-10 mb-20 mx-14">
          <div class="p-4 w-4/5 flex flex-col items-start justify-start">
            <h2 class="font-bold text-4xl">Es Kuwud Denpasar</h2>
            <h3 class="text-red-600 text-2xl">Rp15.000,00</h3>
            <h4 class="text-2xl">Denpasar, Bali</h4>
            <p class="text-transparent">Bintang 1234</p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-8">
              Es Kuwud adalah salah satu minuman khas Bali yang mudah ditemukan.
              Kuwud sendiri dalam Bahasa Bali berarti kelapa. Karena itu,
              minuman segar ini berbahan dasar kelapa dan dipadukan dengan buah
              lainnya sehingga memiliki kandungan nutrisi yang beragam.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base mt-10">Andini | nova.andini@gmail.com</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-1/5 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="../public/img/kuwud removebg.png" alt="" class="" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- ada 2 bagian, atas makanannya, bawah minumannya. masing masing ada deskripsi singkat, harga, lokasi tempat makannya, rating bintang -->
      </section>
      <section id="contact" class="min-h-screen flex justify-center flex-col items-center">
        <div
        class="h-64 w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-fixed relative bg-bottom" style="background-image: url(../public/img/contact.jfif);">
          <div class="right-0 left-0 top-0 bottom-0 bg-black flex flex-col justify-center items-center opacity-65 absolute z-0"></div>
          <div class="absolute z-10 right-0 left-0 top-0 bottom-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded" />
            <h1 class="text-6xl my-3 text-center text-white">Add Your Review</h1>
            <hr class="w-2/6 border-white border-2 border-solid rounded mx-auto"/>
          </div>
        </div>
        <form action="" method="post" class="w-1/2 flex flex-col my-12 shadow-2xl px-14 py-8 bg-black rounded-lg">
          <h1 class="text-4xl my-3 uppercase text-center text-white">
            Form
          </h1>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
            <hr class="border-white border-2 border-solid w-1/3">
            <h2 class="w-1/3 text-lg my-3 uppercase text-center text-white">
              Data Penulis
            </h2>
            <hr class="border-white border-2 border-solid w-1/3">
          </div>
          <label for="" class="text-2xl text-white">Nama</label>
          <input type="text" name="nama" id="nama" class="border-2 border-solid border-white rounded mb-3 p-2"/>
          <label for="" class="text-2xl text-white">Email</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            id="email"
            class="border-2 border-solid border-white rounded mb-3 p-2"
          />
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
            <hr class="border-white border-2 border-solid w-1/3">
            <h2 class="w-1/3 text-lg my-3 uppercase text-center text-white">
              Ulasan Produk
            </h2>
            <hr class="border-white border-2 border-solid w-1/3">
          </div>
          <label for="nama-produk" class="text-2xl text-white">Nama Produk</label>
          <input type="text" name="nama-produk" id="" class="border-2 border-solid border-white rounded mb-3 p-2">
          <label for="harga-produk" class="text-2xl text-white">Harga Produk</label>
          <input type="text" name="harga-produk" id="" class="border-2 border-solid border-white rounded mb-3 p-2">
          <label for="alamat" class="text-2xl text-white">Alamat Toko</label>
          <input type="text" name="alamat" id="" class="border-2 border-solid border-white rounded mb-3 p-2">
          <label for="gambar" class="text-2xl text-white">Foto Produk</label>
          <input type="file" name="gambar" id="" class="mb-3 py-2">
          <label for="ulasan" class="text-2xl text-white">Ulasan</label>
          <textarea
            name="ulasan"
            id=""
            cols="30"
            rows="5"
            class="border-2 border-solid border-white rounded mb-3 p-2"
          ></textarea>
          <button
            type="submit"
            name="submit"
            class="border-white border-solid border-2 text-white block w-28 rounded text-lg self-center p-2 hover:bg-white hover:text-black"
          >
            Submit
          </button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="bg-black px-14">
      <p class="text-center text-white leading-10">Copyright 2024 Andini</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
